name: Amarela

reviews.review_text:
Most scrumptious food I experienced in a while in Goa. Amazing hospitality, beautiful view and top notch food. Pork chops was a winner for me. I also relished chonak and prawn rava fry.
I would skip crab masala cz I've had better in many places. But the above three are a go to.
I tried Singapore sling cocktail too and it was a great option with the food.

A perfect place to enjoy good food with your family and friends in South Goa with a lake view and good enough parking space away from the city this place is silent. A must try for seafood lovers, we tried their Goan fish curry and it delicious. A must visit place.
Very busy, but the service was quick atmosphere is good and food top notch.  Quality and quantity is excellent. Crispy chicken ðŸ‘Œ.

description:
**Amarela: A Culinary Gem in Chinchinim**

Nestled in the serene landscape of Chinchinim, Amarela has garnered an impressive rating of 4.3 from 2,459 reviews, making it a must-visit destination for both locals and tourists. The restaurant is frequently tagged as an epitome of Goan cuisine, with 68 mentions of "goan," 46 references to its picturesque river view, and praise for its "quick service." Seafood aficionados, in particular, are in for a treat with fan-favorite dishes like bombil and prawn rava fry that contribute to its alluring charm.

### Ambiance & Design

As guests step into Amarela, they are greeted by a vibrant atmosphere that effortlessly combines rustic charm with modern elegance. Reviews capture the essence of the restaurantâ€™s dÃ©cor, featuring wooden accents and warm lighting that create a cozy yet refined dining space. The highlight is undoubtedly the breathtaking view of the river, which can be seen from many tables, making each meal a picturesque experience. The tranquil environment is enhanced further by the gentle melodies of background music, providing a soothing accompaniment to your dining experience.

![Amarela Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnRnGz8aLmfNZVQFc8zjGnM_wmpbEKjRSwKHFrQBO3nvq5lNQRl0UJ2QvNg3Q2h3sh5FnVYzFyRymFiSKcnzug9CCZpCLQ7ZjtTpXq840Df98zhhH43eSGo62mYYnncsmVEh2JZwg=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Amarela's menu is a delightful exploration of authentic Goan flavors, with reviews highlighting culinary triumphs such as the pork chops, chonak, and the enticing Goan fish curry. One diner specifically hailed the pork chops as a "winner," while another noted that the restaurantâ€™s seafood offerings are a highlight for those keen on local cuisine. Presentation-wise, dishes are thoughtfully arranged, showcasing vibrant colors and fresh ingredients that beckon the appetite. For those with dietary preferences, the menu demonstrates inclusivity with options catering to various tastes.

The cocktail offerings, particularly the refreshing Singapore Sling, received commendations for pairing beautifully with the rich flavors of the food, further enhancing the dining experience.

![Signature Dishes](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkOQIa_1WMR6F4s2B3Sp0lpCrow-WZ8cA8FmYdJh8t_AL-cGaQfTi95cTypVmldTb8qFYOKkeZV_MTZgYlAfH0YwPn2uM_Ayyxvnai5NYEVUf6z5WY6Vxug-Pxj-J5MtVxAp8qh=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Patrons of Amarela have expressed satisfaction not only with the food but also with the quality of service. The staff is frequently described as friendly and efficient, making for a warm and welcoming dining atmosphere. Even during peak hours, customer reviews reflect that the service remains prompt, allowing for an enjoyable experience without long waits. The restaurant's accessibility is further enhanced by ample parking space, making it a convenient option for families and groups looking to enjoy a leisurely meal.

### Popularity & Reviews

The social media buzz surrounding Amarela reflects a consensus of admiration from customers, who appreciate its dedication to excellence in both cuisine and service. Many reviews emphasize the restaurant as a "must-try," particularly for those who cherish Goan seafood. The enthusiasm is contagious, with a steady stream of patrons being drawn to enjoy a slice of peace along the riverbank while savouring delightful dishes. 

![Food Presentation and Popular Dishes](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdmnuRgnnYFrsaP0O_dkU1BaAn2OeSXwaNyhquvbhy1ADO-N2577lsbDgphE3jE1qE_XqwE7Mh2DH8JU-P7AuDEEdnOE98ahvyMmLW9lDacm4rg2aa-cgShxLPUylWtjUy-wkCpMJA=w375-h563-p)

### Conclusion

In conclusion, Amarela stands out as a culinary haven in Chinchinim, where the combination of delectable Goan cuisine, scenic beauty, and exceptional service creates an unforgettable dining experience. Whether you're a seafood lover or simply seeking a serene spot for family gatherings, Amarela is perfectly poised to meet and exceed your expectations, ensuring that every visit is a memorable one.
